snippet.title: Magic Touch (Nitrome.com) Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay of Magic Touch, a Nitrome minigame created in 2007 about drawing the shapes that appear in balloons to pop them and avoiding the invasion of the knights.
You can play it in: http://www.nitrome.com/games/magictouch/?game=magictouch#.X52f-pBJxPY
I hope you like it!
